parameters: Nothing is spared for the Yume Sakura high school annual festival
不愧是梦樱高校的年度盛会
There's still an hour until it begins, but there's already so many people
明明还有一小时才开始，但现在已经那么多人了
Seems like...all of them came with their friends...
看起来……好像都是和朋友一起过来的……
I should find a suitable place...
Yeah, the stage rehearsal just ended
对啊，舞台排练那边刚忙完
You worked hard...I didn't help much at all...
真是辛苦了……我都没帮上什么忙……
It's alright, they suddenly needed an extra person yesterday, so they came to me
没事没事，他们昨天突然需要多一个人，才找了我
I heard...is it because of Ari's condition?
我也听说了……是因为雅莉同学的事情？
We immediately sent her to the infirmary
我们立刻就把她送到医务室了
Ari pushed herself too hard, she insisted even though she wasn't feeling well
雅莉同学她太勉强自己了，明明身体不舒服还要硬上
Takuya, I'd like to ask you...
About Ari... do you know her well?
雅莉同学她……平时你对她有了解吗？
Nothing, I just wanted to ask
Ari has been in this class for so long, but she doesn't talk to people too often
雅莉同学在这个班里这么长时间，几乎很少和人说话
She feels like a more introverted person...
感觉是个比较内向的人吧……
Aside from Ari, didn't you also have a fever this morning?
且不说雅莉同学，你今天早上不还发烧了吗？
Oh that! I'm fine, I'm fine! I feel a lot better now!
哦那个！没事了，没事了！现在已经好多了！
Really! I can run five laps to prove it!
真的！我现在就能跑五圈证明给你看！
So every time I regret questioning you
所以我每次都要后悔去质疑你
I'm really fine! ! I know my body best! !
真的没事！！我自己最清楚自己的身体了！！
You should've waited for me yesterday...I have umbrella...
你昨天应该等我的……我带了伞……
No, things happened so quickly, I just thought of rushing home
没，事发突然，我就想着赶紧回家了
And I really didn't think it would rain that heavily...
而且我是真没想到会下这么大的雨……
But having said that, the weather forecast said it would be sunny...
不过话说回来，明明天气预报说了晴天的……
Yeah, I also borrowed that umbrella
嗯，那把伞也是我借来的
There are some spare umbrellas at the gym
体育馆那边有些备用的伞
Or else I couldn't even go home
We did the rehersal until very late yesterday
我们昨晚搞排练搞到特别晚
So, what did you do after that?
No choice, I bought another book...
没办法呀，我自己又买多了一本······
You could just watch it online
其实都可以在网上看嘛
I prefer to keep it for reading...
我还是比较喜欢收藏起来看……
Eh, so that's how it is
Unless I'm forced to, I'm really slow when reading and doing homework
除非逼不得已，我看书写作业都会很慢
So that's why you're always the last one to finish the exams?
所以你才老是考试最后一个写完？
Hahaha... that's because I don't know the answers……
哈哈哈……那个是因为我不知道答案……
But I really do read books slowly... Unlike Shio, quantum reading speed
但是我看书确实比较慢……不像汐，你是量子阅读
I'm just average though, like one book a day
我还好啦，一天一本书左右吧
Yeah yeah, the whole world knows that
对对对，全世界都知道了
At best, I don't take the initiative to talk to strangers
我顶多是不太爱主动和陌生人讲话而已
And who plays Otome games in class?
是谁在班里玩乙女游戏的？
How dare you trick me into saying that!
wo xi ni de nao a！
It feels nice, just like this
Is something wrong? Do you want to see a doctor?
出问题了吧？要去看医生吗？
He looked at the fading gray-blue skyline in the distance of the field
他眺望着操场远处逐渐暗淡的灰蓝色天际线
Spoken slowly, without even a hint of a joking tone
缓缓地说了出来，语气中听不出一丝戏谑
The hustle and bustle of Yume Sakura high school
Apart from the scattered lights of school clubs' acitivity room, only the outlines of the undulating buildings can be seen
现在除了星星点点的活动部灯光，只能看见高低起伏的楼宇轮廓
The buzz and roar of jets passing by above, the touch of a sultry evening breeze flowing past my fingertips
空中经过的喷气式飞机的嗡嗡轰鸣，稍带闷热的晚风拂过指尖的触感
The night where the spring equinox approaches, accompanied by the roar of the students
春分将至的夜晚，伴随着周围同学们的嬉闹声
The smell of vigorously growing grass on the field, a sense of security being lightly supported by the warm soil under the soles of my feet
操场上青草旺盛生长的气味，被脚掌心下温暖的泥土轻轻托住的安全感
It's as if everything is reflecting the yearning in my heart right now
仿佛一切都在映衬着此时心中的向往
Even using all of my energy to capture all this
纵使用尽全身的力气去记录这一切
It's still difficult to grasp such an indescribable but coveted scenery
也难以抓住眼下这番难以言喻却又梦寐以求的场景
So taken for granted, so fleeting
如此理所当然，如此转瞬即逝
How can I describe what I'm feeling at this moment?
我该如何形容此刻的感受？
I've been thinking recently...how long can we live like this?
我最近总是在想……这样的生活还能过多久？
Not just high school life, but everything we have now
不只是高中，还有现在的所有一切
I hope it will last really long
But one day, it will all be over won't it？
但总有一天会结束的不是吗？
Let's say, if everything here right now, would last for 1 more minute
假如说，如果现在所有这一切，只剩下最后1分钟
After 1 minute, no matter what happened in the past
这1分钟过后，无论过去发生过什么
No matter how much you miss, how deep the bonds go
即使有再多的思念，再深的羁绊
The daily life in this school, all the feelings of this moment
这所学校日常也好，此刻所有的感受也好
And...all the stories that might happen in the future between Shio and I
还有……我和汐之间所有未来可能发生的故事
After this 1 last minute, everything will end
这1分钟过后，将全部会被宣告停止
From then on, there will be no more interactions between us
从此往后，我们之间不再会有任何交集
We'll each be in different places, having different experiences
各自在不同的地方，有着不同的遭遇
Different trajectories, different worries, different experiences every day
不同的轨迹，不同的烦恼，不同的每一天
If it were Shio...How would you plan to say goodbye?
如果是汐的话……你会打算用什么方式来告别呢？
What I cherish in this moment, everything, bidding farewell in the next second...
此刻我所珍视的，所有一切，都要在下一秒和我告别……
A rising flame, roaring explosion, and then bursting into the most brilliant light
火光升腾，爆炸轰鸣，然后绽放出最灿烂的光芒
This very moment, the school field and teaching building illuminated under the curtain of night
夜幕下的学校操场，教学楼，在这一瞬间被全部照亮
The cheering and joyful screams of the surrounding students coming one after another
周围同学们的欢呼声、尖叫声此起彼伏
烟花，如同一位不速之客
Involuntarily breaking all the tranquility and stiffness of the night sky
不由分说地打破了夜空所有的宁静和死板
In its unforgettable and unpredictable stance, it challenges all common sense
以它最出人意料又难以让人忘却的姿态，挑战着所有的常识
I will utilize all my strength, all my feelings
我会用尽我全部的力气，全部的感情
Leaving the brightest memories for those who care about me, those who love me
为在意我的人，爱我的人，留下最灿烂的回忆
Even if it's sad, even if I'm reluctant to leave...
即使是如此难过，即使是如此不舍……
I will let them see the best of me in that moment
我也会让他们看到我最好的一刻
After a long time, they might forget me
很久之后，或许他们会把我忘却
Or you might not remember things about me
或许你也可能想不起和我的事情了
If I'm forgotten...it will definitely be a sad thing
如果被忘记了的话……也许确实是件伤心的事情
I will use up all my strength and let them see the best of me
我也要竭尽我全部的力气，让他们看到最好的我
Let you see the best of me
Because all I can do, the only thing I can do
因为这是我能够做到的，仅此唯一的
Is to thank them as much as I can
Something that one as cowardly...as ordinary as I am...
是如此懦弱的我……如此不争气的我……
Ah...I feel like I've said some embarrassing things...
啊……感觉说了些丢脸的事情……
Shio is always like this, always in front of me
汐总是这样，总是我的前面
That's why I'm always behind chasing you
所以我才一直在后面追着汐
Wish I could catch up to you someday
真希望有一天能在后面追上你
Hope that I can still spend this summer together with Shio
今年的夏天，也希望能和汐一起渡过呢
Recently I've been worried about gains and losses
最近莫名其妙的有点患得患失了
Are you going to turn into a Chuunibyou Shounen?
你是不是要转型成电波系少年？
Didn't you also say something unexplainable just now?
你刚不也说了莫名其妙的话
Wasn't that because you asked me a strange question?
还不是因为你问我奇怪的问题?
As with previous years, the fireworks festival ended on time at 9 o' clock
如同像往年一样，花火大会准时在9点结束
Takuya didn't say a lot until he left
直到临走之前，塔库亚都没有再多说什么话
Thinking about his matter, I unknowingly walked right up to the door of my house
想着他的事情，不知不觉走到了家门口
Everytime I go home, I always think about strange things
每次回家，总是在想奇奇怪怪的事情
Even if I hit a telephone pole, or walk into a pit
就算在路上撞到电线杆，或者踩到坑里了
I would probably unconciously get up and continue walking forward
估计也会不自觉地爬起来继续往前走
Nothing can interrupt my thought process
没有任何事情可以打断我的思路
For so many years, I haven't carefully observed what was on the side of the road
所以导致这么多年了，也没有仔细观察过到底路边都有些啥
I always forget the scene when I arrive at the door
总是一到家门口就想不起来了
Time to take a bath and head to bed. There will be a full day of activities tomorrow...
先洗个澡睡觉吧，明天还有一天的活动来着……
